      </span>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold leading-tight">The Night She Owned</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-bone-50/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A story of heat, rhythm, and discovery — from Montego Bay’s nights to its unspoken truths.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-sm">
        <span class="text-ember-400">Bruce C Bee</span>
        <span class="text-bone-50/50">•</span>
